1
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:08,460
Where have you taken Tian?

2
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:09,800
What are you planning to do?

3
00:00:09,800 --> 00:00:11,880
If you handle this matter well,

4
00:00:12,320 --> 00:00:16,000
I promise I'll never come after Tian again.

5
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:19,050
He used Tian to threaten me.

6
00:00:20,440 --> 00:00:21,200
At first,

7
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:24,000
I thought he only wanted to use

8
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:26,000
my connections with the Situ family

9
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:30,160
to help the Sun family establish themselves in Tongzhou.

10
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:31,820
But who would have thought

11
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:35,760
he would mix ghost poppy into the ingredients,

12
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:39,040
using this to control more food suppliers in Tongzhou

13
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:42,400
and gradually take over the Situ family's business.

14
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:44,440
Then why didn't you report this to the authorities?

15
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:45,080
Report it?

16
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:47,560
You think I haven't thought of that?

17
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:49,160
But Sun Ding is very cunning.

18
00:00:49,400 --> 00:00:51,520
I was the face of all transactions,

19
00:00:52,400 --> 00:00:54,400
but the goods never passed through my hands.

20
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:56,660
I never knew the source of the ghost poppy

21
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:58,560
or where the food was processed.

22
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:00,320
Without solid evidence,

23
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:02,440
how could I challenge the Sun family?

24
00:01:02,440 --> 00:01:03,560
Young Master Sun's behavior

25
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:05,720
is both ridiculous and suspicious.

26
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:07,930
I don't understand,

27
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:10,039
why did you send people to kill us?

28
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:19,200
The people who tried to kill you were sent by Sun Ding.

29
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,460
I couldn't intervene.

30
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:26,560
Until that day when I saw the butler leave,

31
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:30,280
I deliberately showed myself so Miss Ruting would see me.

32
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:33,240
Because I knew she was close to Yun'er,

33
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,539
if she saw me at the Sun residence,

34
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:37,560
she would certainly become suspicious

35
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:40,080
and would definitely investigate thoroughly.

36
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,880
That night, if it weren't for me,

37
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:44,330
you would have been poisoned to death.

38
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,890
So you were the one who saved us.

39
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:54,840
Yun'er told me

40
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:57,420
that by Miss Ruting's side

41
00:01:57,960 --> 00:02:00,020
there was a young man named Chu Bufan.

42
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:02,400
He's righteous and chivalrous,

43
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,860
skilled at solving cases.

44
00:02:03,880 --> 00:02:05,080
After arriving in Tongzhou,

45
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:08,000
he helped the Imperial Guard solve the iron ore case,

46
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:10,860
and exposed the darkness in the painting workshop.

47
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,920
Master Chu,

48
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:15,600
the ghost poppy matter concerns the safety of the common people,

49
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:18,200
Sun Ding must face the punishment he deserves.

50
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,140
We need comprehensive evidence,

51
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,500
but I can't do it alone.

52
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,890
What do you need me to do?

53
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,940
I recently discovered a place

54
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:33,440
that's very likely storing ghost poppies.

55
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:36,600
There are too many guards for me to get close and confirm.

56
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:38,079
If we can catch them red-handed,

57
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:40,210
we can certainly bring him to justice.

58
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,240
An Ruolai.

59
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,520
I'll trust you this once.

60
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,820
You'd better not have any other motives.

61
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,840
Don't take any lives during this operation.

62
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:06,640
Rest assured.

63
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,560
Brothers, let's have another drink.

64
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,280
Come, drink up!

65
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,560
Carry on.

66
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:58,930
