78
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,680
Thank you,

79
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,409
my pleasure.

80
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,240
Have a drink, sir.

81
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:55,080
Good.

82
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,800
What do you want?

83
