How dare you, Sun Ding!

84
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,280
You've been selling poisonous ingredients,

85
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,040
harming the people of Tongzhou,

86
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,200
Today I'm ordered to arrest you.

87
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,370
Ridiculous!

88
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:16,240
My family has been in business for generations,

89
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:18,080
we've never broken any laws.

90
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,880
