91
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,500
and slandering my family.

92
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,320
Whether you've broken the law or not,

93
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,720
we'll discuss it at the magistrate's office.

94
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,520
Take him away.

95
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,720
I won't go! I won't go!

96
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,720
That's An Ruolai.

97
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,920
I'm innocent!

98
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,720
You've got the wrong person!

99
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,730
You've arrested the wrong person!

100
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,240
You shameless merchant!

101
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,320
How dare you sell poisonous ingredients,

102
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,600
the evidence is irrefutable.

103
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,000
Take him away.

104
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,640
Yes, sir.

105
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,600
This can't be!

106
00:05:58,400 --> 00:05:59,680
Sir! Sir!

107
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,140
What are you doing?

108
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,040
Officer, you can't take that!

109
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,970
Get out of my way!

110
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:04,640
Sir,

111
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,080
I'm innocent, sir!

112
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,080
Sir,

113
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,280
save it for the court.

114
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:13,920
No,

115
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,450
my business is legitimate!

116
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,200
I'm innocent!

117
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:19,440
I'm innocent! Wrongfully accused!

118
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:20,500
This is injustice!

119
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,720
Sun Ding.

120
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,920
You've been hoarding large quantities of ghost millet fruit,

121
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,780
selling poisonous ingredients,

122
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:34,560
harming innocent people,

123
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,520
and disrupting the marketplace in Tongzhou.

124
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:38,920
Do you admit to your crimes?

125
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,159
Your Honor, please see clearly,

126
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:44,320
these accusations are all false.

127
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,200
I'm merely a merchant,

128
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:49,120
how could I have done such harmful things?

129
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:51,220
All these wrongdoings

130
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,760
were committed by my unfilial son,

131
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,000
An Ruolai.

132
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,880
He deceived me.

133
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,640
I was simply misled

134
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,680
and knew nothing about it.

135
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,440
Sun Ding,

136
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,120
the evidence is conclusive,

137
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:06,040
yet you continue to make excuses

138
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:09,640
and push all blame onto others.

139
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,200
According to our investigation,

140
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,680
your Sun family in Jizhou

141
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:15,410
has been secretly growing ghost poppies,

142
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,240
in massive quantities,

143
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,400
earning ill-gotten gains.

144
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,400
Are these false accusations as well?

145
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,180
Your Honor,

146
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,600
I am an old man

147
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:29,400
who never inquires about the details of our business.

148
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:32,560
An Ruolai manages everything,

149
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:35,480
and I had no idea he was using my name

150
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:38,080
to commit such harmful deeds.

151
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,240
Your Honor,

152
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:52,200
here are the ledgers and supply orders showing Sun Ding's conspiracy to grow ghost poppies

153
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:54,360
and harm the people.

154
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:08,280
These ledgers and contracts

155
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,840
clearly document

156
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:12,120
your cultivation and sale of ghost poppies,

157
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,560
and they bear your seal.

158
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:16,900
What else do you have to say for yourself?

159
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,160
An Ruolai.

160
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,690
You ungrateful son.

161
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:26,800
If my son Sun Anyang hadn't died prematurely,

162
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:27,880
I would never have acknowledged

163
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:31,120
a bastard of such lowly birth as you.

164
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:35,000
You'll end up just like your worthless mother,

165
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:37,080
meeting a miserable end,

166
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:37,760
Sun Ding.

167
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:41,289
My mother lived a virtuous life until you ruined her.

168
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,039
You have no right to even speak of her.

169
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:45,300
The criminal Sun Ding,

170
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,960
with all witnesses and evidence present,

171
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:50,000
has committed unforgivable crimes.

172
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,840
According to the laws of the Great Ming,

173
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,360
he shall be beheaded in public,

174
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,090
to serve as a warning to others.

175
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:55,880
Guards!

176
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:56,960
Take him away.

177
00:08:57,760 --> 00:08:59,200
Your Honor.

178
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,280
Your Honor, please leave.

179
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:02,040
Your Honor, spare my life!

180
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,080
Your Honor, please hurry!

181
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:05,440
Your Honor, have mercy!

182
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,760
Excuse me,

183
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:31,000
do you have fresh deer antler here?

184
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,640
Yes,

185
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,200
this way, miss.

186
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:51,940
Please take a look,

187
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:53,760
this is golden-edged plum blossom antler,

188
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:55,520
sourced from the northern cold regions,

189
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,650
taken from two-year-old strong deer,

190
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:00,280
with extremely rich medicinal properties.

191
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:00,880
Look.

192
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:04,160
The texture is firm and delicate with a rich red color,

193
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:05,840
making it a premium choice,

194
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:10,700
especially good for nourishing vitality, enriching blood, and strengthening bones.

195
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,200
If you're looking for

196
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,460
warming and nourishing effects,

197
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,240
we also have this.

198
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,640
The spotted deer antler has mild properties,

199
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:24,720
suitable for women's daily health maintenance and replenishing energy,

200
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:26,450
and won't cause internal heat.

201
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:30,200
You know quite a lot for an apprentice.

202
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,640
I've been poor since childhood,

203
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:34,840
with no one to rely on,

204
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:37,720
but I understand that without connections, learning more

205
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:39,040
will always be beneficial.

206
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:40,700
I can see you're trustworthy,

207
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,040
work well in my Situ family in the future,

208
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:45,170
and you'll surely achieve something.

209
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,000
May I ask your name, miss?

210
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,640
My name is Situ Chenyun.

211
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,160
Yun'er.

212
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,320
I miss you so much.

213
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,600
Do you know

214
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:29,040
I cannot bear all this by myself.

215
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:35,720
I still need to get a clear answer from him.

216
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,000
I just feel that

217
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:40,200
Sister Yun's matter hasn't been fully explained.

218
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:45,560
An Ruolai.

219
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:46,720
An Ruolai.

220
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,580
He's taken poison.

221
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,620
Quickly take him to the young master.

222
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,280
Do you think An Ruolai

223
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:09,080
truly failed Sister Yun?

224
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,880
Seeing him kneeling at Sister Yun's grave,

225
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,400
crying so heartbrokenly.

226
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,730
The matters of the heart

227
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:17,280
are truly unfathomable.

228
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:19,420
An Ruolai's behavior,

229
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,440
rather than seeming like repentance,

230
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,360
is more like

231
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:24,520
someone unable to bear

232
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:26,280
the pain of losing his beloved.

233
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:30,400
I believe his feelings for your Sister Yun

234
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:33,530
must have been genuine without doubt.

235
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:35,520
If he truly loved Sister Yun,

236
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:38,040
why would he get involved in the Sun family's conspiracy?

237
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,700
What exactly was he planning?

238
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,720
There must be

239
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:44,880
hidden circumstances we don't yet know about.

240
00:12:45,920 --> 00:12:47,000
In matters of love,

241
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:49,650
everyone protects it in their own way.

242
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:51,720
Sometimes we shouldn't use our own perspective

243
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:54,050
to measure the depth of others' feelings.

244
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:03,520
But true love

245
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:06,160
should be mutual trust and honesty,

246
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:08,900
not deceiving each other in the name of love.

247
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:11,660
Someone as perceptive as Sister Yun,

248
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:14,820
if she knew An Ruolai was hiding something from her,

249
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:17,520
would be terribly disappointed.

250
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:24,360
Ruting.

251
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:30,250
Everyone has dark corners in their heart.

252
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:32,220
Painful memories of the past,

253
00:13:32,560 --> 00:13:34,620
or secrets too difficult to speak of.

254
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:37,000
Keeping secrets from a loved one

255
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,920
might be unavoidable,

256
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:40,680
or perhaps

257
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:44,120
not wanting to drag them into darkness.

258
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:47,280
Now that Miss Situ has passed away,

259
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,720
whether An Ruolai ever kept secrets from her

260
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,720
remains unknown,

261
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:53,290
we shouldn't rush to conclusions.

262
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:55,900
What about you?

263
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,940
Do you also have painful memories

264
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:02,180
or secrets unknown to others?

265
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:03,410
I... well...

266
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:05,520
