267
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:07,800
How did the conversation turn to me?

268
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:12,000
So you do have secrets.

269
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,440
Ruting.

270
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:18,640
My past isn't worth mentioning.

271
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:19,680
Let's focus

272
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,560
on saving An Ruolai instead.

273
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:33,920
Fortunately, the poisoning wasn't severe

274
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:35,320
and treatment was prompt,

275
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,250
so there's no serious concern now.

276
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:40,360
You two talk. I'll go prepare the medicine.

277
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:45,000
An Ruolai.

278
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,240
If you're so heartbroken,

279
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,840
why did you betray Sister Yun

280
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:50,720
and cause her untimely death?

281
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,160
How dare you cry here?

282
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:54,320
I never betrayed Yun'er.

283
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,360
